data.description: Tired of rising rent prices? Own for less than rent for this over free standing Condo with1500 square feet of living space which includes 3 bedrooms, 2 and a half bath, with front porch, patio and attached 2 car garage. The seller in the last 3 years has made many updates, ceramic tile floor, granite look countertop, deep sink with goose neck faucet, and garden disposal. New fireplace mantle and ceramic tile around fireplace. Note refregerator and stove do not stay.
